reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars work well for my kitchenaid dishwasher
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I bought it to replace the lower rack wheels of my kitchenaid dishwasher. Installation is super easy about 3 minutes. They snap right into place and have functioned very well till now. Great replacement for my old kitchenaid wheels and very reasonably priced.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits perfect on Whirlpool Dishwasher
reviews.reviewText: These wheels were easy to install and look like a perfect replacement for the wheels on a Whirlpool Dishwasher. They look like they will be at least as durable as the original wheels and are much cheaper.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Simple installation, smooth operation
reviews.reviewText: I couldn’t be happier with these. They installed super quickly and easily. Worked like a charm. They are smooth and seem to be high quality. They have been installed over a month and show no signs of wear even with heavy use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Work well, easy to install
reviews.reviewText: Installed the new wheels in just a couple minutes, they work great. Would purchase again if needed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars All Plastic is the way to go
reviews.reviewText: Purchased these after a prior replacement that used a metal rivet & bolt where the wheel connects to the base rusted and subsequently broke a blade off the pump in my dishwasher. This all plastic one is holding up really well like the OEM part did for nearly a decade.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Some of the wheels had broken off of my dishwasher bottom rack. These replacements were very easy to install and are working great so far (about a month). Price was excellent.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Work Great Why Pay More
reviews.reviewText: Got them yesterday install them this morning and the wheels roll just fine There are so many choices that all appear to be about the same and I was nervous because this one didn’t have that many reviews and it was newer but I think they have solved some of the problems that the other products available have had per their one star reviews.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great replacement product
reviews.reviewText: The replacement wheels were easy to install and our dishwasher is just like new.
